GtkAda 2.4.0 release
--------------------

GtkAda is an Ada95 graphical toolkit based on Gtk+. It allows you
to develop graphical applications in Ada95 using Gtk+.

The primary download site is http://libre.act-europe.fr/GtkAda

This version is suitable for use with Gtk+ 2.2.1 and above.

New features in 2.4.0:

- Improvements in GtkAda.MDI
- Compatible with Gtk+ 2.4.x
- Compatible with latest Ada AIs

